sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant MMSvc as ModelMesh Service<br/>8008/TCP
    participant Proxy as rest-proxy Sidecar<br/>8008/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant MMGRPC as ModelMesh gRPC<br/>localhost:8033/TCP
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 1: REST Inference Request

    Client->>MMSvc: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional TLS
    MMSvc->>Proxy: Route to pod<br/>8008/TCP
    Note over Proxy: CustomJSONPb unmarshals<br/>JSON tensor data<br/>(BOOL, INT8-64, FP16-64, BYTES)
    Note over Proxy: gRPC-Gateway translates<br/>REST → gRPC ModelInfer
    Proxy->>MMGRPC: gRPC ModelInfer()<br/>Optional TLS, Max 16MB
    MMGRPC->>Runtime: Forward to model runtime<br/>gRPC
    Runtime-->>MMGRPC: InferResponse
    MMGRPC-->>Proxy: gRPC ModelInferResponse
    Note over Proxy: CustomJSONPb marshals<br/>response tensor data to JSON
    Proxy-->>MMSvc: HTTP 200 JSON Response
    MMSvc-->>Client: Inference Result

    Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Metadata Request

    Client->>MMSvc: GET /v2/models/{name}<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    MMSvc->>Proxy: Route to pod<br/>8008/TCP
    Note over Proxy: gRPC-Gateway translates<br/>REST → gRPC ModelMetadata
    Proxy->>MMGRPC: gRPC ModelMetadata()<br/>localhost:8033
    MMGRPC-->>Proxy: ModelMetadataResponse
    Proxy-->>MMSvc: HTTP 200 JSON
    MMSvc-->>Client: Model Metadata
